<view class="page-shell" wx:if="{{ready}}" id="settings-view">
  <view class="page-title">设置</view>
  <view class="section"><view class="row-between section-title"><view><image class="icon" src="/assets/icons/members.svg" />家庭成员</view><button class="button-primary button-small" bindtap="addMember" id="settings-add-member">新增成员</button></view><view class="card member-list"><view class="member-row" wx:for="{{members}}" wx:key="id"><view class="avatar avatar-{{item.colorName}}">{{item.initial}}</view><text class="member-name" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="editMember">{{item.name}}</text><button class="mini" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-delta="-1" bindtap="moveMember" disabled="{{index === 0}}">↑</button><button class="mini" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-delta="1" bindtap="moveMember" disabled="{{index === members.length - 1}}">↓</button><button class="mini danger" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="deleteMember">删除</button></view></view></view>
  <view class="section card"><view class="section-title">应用内提醒</view><text class="reminder-note">提醒只在小程序打开或回到前台时显示，不会在后台发送微信通知。</text><view class="setting-row"><text>启用提醒</text><switch checked="{{reminderEnabled}}" color="#2E7D5B" bindchange="updateReminderEnabled" /></view><view class="setting-row"><text>每日任务汇总</text><picker mode="time" value="{{dailyTime}}" bindchange="updateDailyTime"><view class="time">{{dailyTime}}</view></picker></view><view class="setting-row"><text>逾期任务提醒</text><picker mode="time" value="{{overdueTime}}" bindchange="updateOverdueTime"><view class="time">{{overdueTime}}</view></picker></view></view>
  <view class="section card"><view class="section-title">数据管理</view><view class="row-between"><view><text class="storage-title">本地存储</text><text class="storage {{storageWarning ? 'danger' : ''}}">{{storageText}}</text></view><image class="data-icon" src="/assets/icons/history.svg" /></view><text class="backup-note">建议定期导出 JSON。微信清理缓存或删除小程序后，本地数据可能丢失。</text><view class="backup-actions"><button class="button-primary" bindtap="exportBackup" id="data-export-backup">导出备份</button><button class="button-plain" bindtap="importBackup" id="data-import-backup">恢复备份</button></view></view>
</view>
